      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable and well-maintained ride that's perfect for your daily commute! This vehicle is in good condition, showing clear signs of consistent care and attention over the years. It drives smoothly and remains a solid, reliable choice for anyone looking for a quality car that's ready for the road ahead!",
