    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owners. The engine starts up easily and runs smoothly, while the transmission shifts through all gears as expected with no hesitations. The interior is clean with only minor signs of wear, and the exterior paint retains a nice shine, though you may find a few small chips from normal road use. All electronics and safety features are fully operational, making this a reliable and ready-to-drive option for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
